header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - Wichita Region - 1st Round

videos.description: Rae Burrell steps in front of the pass and gets the steal for the layup, forcing a Buffalo timeout.

videos.headline: Burrell forces a Buffalo timeout with a steal and score

videos.description: Buffalo's Georgia Woolley ends the first quarter in style with a 3-pointer that bounces around on the rim.

videos.headline: Buffalo takes the lead after a buzzer-beater 3

videos.description: Tennessee guard Jordan Walker shakes the defense with a sweet hesitation move and a finish in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jordan Walker’s sweet hesitation leads to Tennessee bucket) 2022/03/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Walker's sweet hesitation leads to Tennessee bucket

videos.description: Buffalo guard Georgia Woolley reads the passing lane and gets the steal and layup.

videos.headline: Buffalo's Woolley picks off the pass for an easy layup

videos.description: Buffalo guard Dyaisha Fair gets out in transition and makes the beautiful pass to Summer Hemphill for the easy basket.

videos.headline: Buffalo's Fair drops dime to Hemphill for the layup

videos.description: Jordan Walker makes a sweet move in the lane before banking in the floater right as the third-quarter buzzer goes off.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Jordan Walker shakes defender for floater at third-quarter buzzer) 2022/03/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Walker shakes defender for floater at third-quarter buzzer

videos.description: Tennesee's Rae Burrell knocks down the 3-pointer, putting the Volunteers up 10 in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Burrell's 3 gives Tennessee their first double-digit lead of the day

videos.description: Tennessee gets a big fourth quarter as they take down Buffalo 80-67 to advance to the Round of 32.
